{"name":"数据渲染","id":"编程语言-JavaScript-Vue-数据渲染","content":"# 数据渲染\n\n## 插值表达式\n\n```javascript\n{{ number + 1 }}\n{{ ok ? 'YES' : 'NO' }}\n```\n\n```html\n<div v-text=\"message\"></div><!--会进行HTML转义-->\n<div v-html=\"message\"></div>\n<!-- 完整语法 -->\n<a v-bind:href=\"url\">...</a>\n<!-- 缩写 -->\n<a :href=\"url\">...</a>\n```\n\n## 表单绑定\n\n```html\n<!-- 绑定输入域 -->\n<input type=\"text\" v-model=\"user.password\"/>\n<!-- 绑定单选框 -->\n<input type=\"radio\" id=\"male\" value=\"1\" v-model='gender'>\n<input type=\"radio\" id=\"female\" value=\"2\" v-model='gender'>\n<!-- 绑定复选框 hobby要定义成数组，否则不能多选 -->\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"ball\" value=\"1\" v-model='hobby'>\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"sing\" value=\"2\" v-model='hobby'>\n<input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"code\" value=\"3\" v-model='hobby'>\n<!-- 绑定下拉框,occupation必须是数组 -->\n<select v-model='occupation' multiple>\n    <option value=\"0\">请选择职业...</option>\n    <option value=\"1\">教师</option>\n    <option value=\"2\">软件工程师</option>\n    <option value=\"3\">律师</option>\n</select>\n```\n\n### 修饰符\n\n```html\n<!-- .number:转换为数值 -->\n<input type=\"text\" v-model.number=\"value\">\n<!-- .trim:去掉首尾空格 -->\n<input type=\"text\" v-model.trim=\"value\">\n<!-- .lazy:在失去焦点 或者 按下回车键时才更新 -->\n<input type=\"text\" v-model.lazy=\"value\">\n```\n\n## 列表渲染\n\n- 渲染list\n\n```html\n<li v-for=\"(value,index) in list\" :key=\"value.id\">{{value}} and {{index}}</li>\n```\n\n- 渲染对象\n\n```html\n<ul>\n  <li v-for=\"(value,key,index) in object\">\n    {{key}} : {{ value }}\n  </li>\n</ul>\n```\n\n## 条件渲染\n\n### v-if\n\n```html\n<!--  flag为true时才被<渲染> -->\n<span v-if=\"flag\">content</span>\n```\n\n- v-else\n\n```html\n<div v-if=\"Math.random() > 0.5\">\n  Now you see me\n</div>\n<div v-else>\n  Now you don't\n</div>\n```\n\n- v-else-if\n\n```html\n<div v-if=\"type === 'A'\">\n  A\n</div>\n<div v-else-if=\"type === 'B'\">\n  B\n</div>\n<div v-else-if=\"type === 'C'\">\n  C\n</div>\n<div v-else>\n  Not A/B/C\n</div>\n```\n\n### v-show\n\n```html\n<!--  flag为true时才被<显示> -->\n<span v-show=\"flag\">content</span>\n```\n\n## 样式绑定\n\n- 绑定class\n\n```html\n<!-- 当isActive为true时，这个标签就会增加active这个类，反之会删除active这个类 -->\n<h2 :class=\"{ 'active': isActive }\">home</h2>\n<h2 :class=\"{ active: isActive }\">home</h2>\n```\n\n**数组语法**\n\n```html\n<div v-bind:class=\"[activeClass, errorClass]\"></div>\n```\n```js\ndata: {\n  activeClass: 'active',\n  errorClass: 'text-danger'\n}\n```\n\n渲染为\n\n```html\n<div class=\"active text-danger\"></div>\n```\n\n- 绑定style\n\n拼接字符串\n\n```html\n<div v-bind:style=\"{ color: activeColor, fontSize: fontSize + 'px' }\"></div>\n```\n\n```js\ndata: {\n  activeColor: 'red',\n  fontSize: 30\n}\n```\n\n样式对象\n\n```html\n<div v-bind:style=\"styleObject\"></div>\n```\n\n```js\ndata: {\n  styleObject: {\n    color: 'red',\n    fontSize: '13px'\n  }\n}\n```\n","metadata":"","hasMoreCommit":false,"totalCommits":4,"commitList":[{"date":"2021-09-13T16:19:26+08:00","author":"cjiping","message":"✏更新 Vue 数据渲染","hash":"d761b3279bf1dfac0daf0682d58232f1fc204d7c"},{"date":"2020-03-19T09:38:36+08:00","author":"MY","message":"更新 vue表单绑定","hash":"f00be9e845c61e20f6030314d25db68c7bc18813"},{"date":"2020-02-14T21:53:58+08:00","author":"MY","message":"完成笔记结构重构","hash":"fa76a092bde3bf674471ba101d7e1d1dd2c7108b"},{"date":"2020-02-05T21:02:52+08:00","author":"MY","message":"重构vue","hash":"a5c325817abd7044d8ca02694aa967ee06969c7d"}],"createTime":"2020-02-05T21:02:52+08:00"}